---
import WireframeLayout from '../../layouts/WireframeLayout.astro';
---

<WireframeLayout title="NYC Travel">
  <header>
    <nav class="main-nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Chez Sargaux</a>
      <a href="/nyc" class="back-link">&larr; Back to NYC</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h1>Travel</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Getting to and around NYC</p>

    <section class="travel-sections">
      <!-- Hotels -->
      <div class="travel-card">
        <h2>Hotels</h2>
        <p>Suggested accommodations near the venues:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Hotel TBD</strong> — Near dinner venue</li>
          <li><strong>Hotel TBD</strong> — Near dancing venue</li>
          <li><strong>Budget Option TBD</strong> — Nearby neighborhood</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="placeholder-note">Room block details coming soon</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Getting There -->
      <div class="travel-card">
        <h2>Getting There</h2>

        <h3>By Air</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>JFK</strong> — AirTrain + subway, ~60-75 min to Manhattan</li>
          <li><strong>LGA</strong> — Taxi/rideshare or Q70 bus + subway, ~30-45 min</li>
          <li><strong>EWR</strong> — AirTrain + NJ Transit to Penn Station, ~45-60 min</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>By Train</h3>
        <p>Amtrak arrives at Penn Station (Midtown) or Moynihan Train Hall.</p>

        <h3>By Bus</h3>
        <p>Multiple bus services arrive at Port Authority Bus Terminal (42nd St):</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Greyhound</strong> — Major cities nationwide</li>
          <li><strong>FlixBus</strong> — Budget option, East Coast cities</li>
          <li><strong>Megabus</strong> — Budget option, often stops at 34th St</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Getting Around -->
      <div class="travel-card">
        <h2>Getting Around</h2>

        <h3>MTA Subway</h3>
        <p>New York's subway runs 24/7 and is the fastest way to get around Manhattan.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Single ride: $2.90 (tap contactless or use OMNY)</li>
          <li>Download the <strong>MTA app</strong> for real-time arrivals</li>
          <li>Google Maps and Apple Maps have excellent subway directions</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="placeholder-note">Nearest subway stations to venues TBD</p>

        <h3>Rideshare & Taxi</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Uber and Lyft widely available</li>
          <li>Yellow cabs can be hailed on the street</li>
          <li>Expect 20-40 min travel times depending on traffic</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- While You're Here -->
      <div class="travel-card">
        <h2>While You're Here</h2>
        <p>Columbus Day Weekend is a great time to explore NYC's world-class museums and exhibitions:</p>

        <h3>Museums</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>The Met</strong> — Fifth Avenue, suggested donation admission</li>
          <li><strong>MoMA</strong> — Midtown, modern & contemporary art</li>
          <li><strong>Whitney</strong> — Meatpacking District, American art</li>
          <li><strong>Natural History</strong> — Upper West Side, great for all ages</li>
          <li><strong>Guggenheim</strong> — Upper East Side, iconic architecture</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Exhibitions & Experiences</h3>
        <p class="placeholder-note">Current exhibitions for October 2026 TBD — check museum websites closer to date</p>

        <h3>Neighborhoods to Explore</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>West Village</strong> — Charming streets, cafes, boutiques</li>
          <li><strong>SoHo</strong> — Shopping, galleries, cast-iron architecture</li>
          <li><strong>High Line</strong> — Elevated park, great for a walk</li>
          <li><strong>Central Park</strong> — Fall foliage should be beautiful</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Sam Gross</p>
  </footer>
</WireframeLayout>

<style>
  header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .main-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #666;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  main {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .travel-sections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .travel-card {
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .travel-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .travel-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .travel-card h3:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .travel-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .travel-card ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .travel-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .placeholder-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  footer p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #888;
  }
</style>
